messages.title: Building a brighter future for Sutton, Cheam & Worcester Park
messages.content: Hina Bokhari is a proven local champion who will always put Sutton, Cheam & Worcester Park first.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Family live in Sutton and she has taught in Sutton schools - she will always put Sutton, Cheam and Worcester Park first.
Committed to fighting Brexit to protect local jobs, to tackle the climate emergency and to grow the economy.
A proven campaigner against harmful cuts and a supporter of fair funding for our schools.
